                <p>本周推荐了超过 30 款值得推荐的游戏，这一周平台类游戏居多。</p><p>不过也有另类，比如有款很新鲜的 <a href="https://indienova.com/game/make-me-lag" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Make Me LAG</a>，居然是要让电脑变慢，造成游戏丢帧才能过关，也算是脑洞大开了……</p><p>另外我们的即将发行页面还在准备中，您时不时可以<a href="https://indienova.com/gamedb/releases" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">来这里看看</a>，因为会随时添加这个列表中缺失的游戏。</p><h4>Dininho Adventures</h4><p>关键字：冒险、平台游戏</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/09（暂无中文）</p><p>在一场可能是您人生中最英勇的冒险中帮助 Dininho（迪尼尼奥）！</p><p>只有真正邪恶的人才会做出这样冷酷的事情：从毫无防备的恐龙妈妈那里偷恐龙蛋！Dininho 不会让它发生的！探索这个色彩斑且危险的世界，营救所有手无寸铁的婴儿。但是要小心，“他”将在每条路的尽头等着你。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-dino2014Vo.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3625874_P0rEYQ.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3625874_6cLRXi.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3625874_Ebe05G.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1230760/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Horizon's Gate</h4><p>Horizon's Gate</p><p>关键字：角色扮演、冒险、策略、探索、开放世界</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/10（暂无中文）</p><p>以探索家，商人，或者私掠者者的身份远航 Eral。揭开 Dominio 背叛的秘密——或者干脆到处航行自己进行航海大冒险。一切都取决于您自己。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/gif-gate_lIrqYeqX.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3254580_7MaFYk.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3254580_Lg9yX8.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3254580_LQCaPl.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1224290/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Axegend（战斧传说）</h4><p>关键字：冒险、角色扮演、策略、模拟、虚拟现实</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/10（<strong>中文支持</strong>）</p><p><em>Axegend VR</em> 是一款类 Roguelike 的动作策略冒险游戏，在 Axegend 的世界中，你将扮演一位全能的骑士，为了拯救公主，无所不用其极。不管是雨伞、轮胎、回旋镖、斧头、灯管等，都可以当做是武器，甚至连猪都带上了……游戏中融合多种多样的元素，紧张刺激，趣味滑稽，且不会不协调。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/gif-Axegend_SCribONi.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3498727_L3sYf6.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3498727_NNwiBK.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3498727_sEY0Qo.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1153460/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>The Escaper</h4><p>关键字：冒险、隐藏物体、物理、解谜</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/10（暂无中文）</p><p><em>The Escaper</em> 是一款具有实时 3D 图形的新型密室逃生游戏，它将挑战您的技能和智力！</p><p>发现隐藏的线索并解决具有挑战性的基于物理的难题，在时间耗尽之前逃脱。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3499487_vyIHqk.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3499487_CENIts.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3499487_mYiu9g.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1234520/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Ragdoll Party Online</h4><p>关键字：模拟、在线合作、建造、沙盒、物理</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/10（暂无中文）EA</p><p>在沙盒模式下与您的朋友们在线创建关卡，玩迷你游戏。布娃娃、开车、乘坐喷射器飞行、放屁高飞、投掷手榴弹…… 可以使用超过 45 种物品建立自己的关卡。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/gif-ragdoll_hBRdeKGV.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3500099_ccyqCa.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3500099_mvGY0X.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3500099_KBTl55.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1228910/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Serin Fate</h4><p>关键字：冒险、角色扮演、沙盒、探索</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/10（暂无中文）EA</p><p><em>Serin Fate</em> 是一款 RPG，灵感来自 <em>Pokemon</em>，<em>Harvest Moon</em>，<em>Runescape</em> 和 <em>Chrono Trigger</em> 等经典游戏。</p><p>命运之石将您变成了女巫。所以您现在该学习一些魔法，整理您的学徒小屋，然后干上几仗！</p><p>掌握新的咒语，找到材料和一些独特的朋友，您能勇敢面对这片土地吗？还是会有很多危险的……Chimera Castle 正有麻烦事在发生，怪物也开始在大地上漫游，所以您可能想在晚上呆在屋里……</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-Serin2391nP.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3610225_TKMvT7.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3610225_kkOhad.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3610225_DRa8sK.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1070860/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Climbros（攀登者）</h4><p>关键字：动作、冒险、欢乐</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/10（暂无中文）</p><p><em>Climbros</em> 是一款令人上瘾的二维街机游戏，您可以在其中进行攀爬。您可以选择单人游戏模式，也可以在局部合作模式下与一群朋友玩。</p><p>惊喜、娱乐、无助、喜悦、满足──各式各样您预期的情绪都将发生。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-climb3692Tl.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3612423_9XRNrg.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3612423_iXYzqe.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3612423_5c0IYO.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1084710/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Ori and the Will of the Wisps</h4><p>关键字：动作、类银河战士恶魔城、唯美、氛围、剧情丰富</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/11（<strong>中文支持</strong>）</p><p>继打造拿下超过 50 个奖项和提名、备受赞誉的冒险游戏 <em>Ori and the Blind Forest</em> 后，制作团队又献上万众期待的续作：<em>Ori and the Will of the Wisps</em>。</p><p>进入辽阔又奇异的世界，展开全新冒险之旅，您将在探索过程中遭遇巨大的敌人和艰钜的谜题，最终揭开奥里的天命。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/gif-ori_q4K0UtX9.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3146594_ntD3SD.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3146594_XCNv81.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3146594_ED8bAq.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1057090/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Victory Road</h4><p>关键字：体育、模拟、策略、暴力</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/11（暂无中文）EA</p><p><em>Victory Road</em> 是一个拳击模拟器，不过这次您是扮演教练的角色，而不是拳击手！</p><p>作为教练，您拳手的职业生涯以及他一生的命运都掌握在您的手中。将您的拳击手素质不断提高，并利用各种策略来登上排名榜。</p><p>看上去，要比 <em>Punch Club</em> 更加专业向一些。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/gif-Victory_H9WwsUh2.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3252949_81NGn5.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3252949_8rRYkW.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3252949_RjWfuE.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1002430/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Dreadlands</h4><p>关键字：策略、回合制战术</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/11（暂无中文）EA</p><p><em>Dreadlands</em> 是一种回合制小规模战略游戏，玩家在其中控制一群不称职的不法之徒和雇佣军们，在末世环境中为生存和霸权而战，探索这个世界上众多不同地域。</p><p>玩家可以从不同派系中挑选您的队伍，这些派系都具有截然不同的游戏风格、知识和表现。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/gif-dreadlands_nlnZHy8f.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3518059_FFOz3D.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3518059_jwbupA.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3518059_rsbLY0.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1054690/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Floppy Heroes 2</h4><p>关键字：动作、奇幻、体素、物理、多人</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/11（暂无中文）EA</p><p><em>Floppy Heroes 2</em> 建立在上一代的基础之上，提供了可肢解的布娃娃物理系统，是一款可以同乐的乱斗游戏。</p><p>游戏包括有种类繁多的武器和装甲、基于体素的物品创建器、简单的操作以及最多 8 个玩家的自定义战斗！</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/gif-floppy_Tz3iiXYK.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3518954_0xqcLA.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3518954_7lD8v8.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3518954_sQg2Rh.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1254150/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>CATharsis</h4><p>关键字：休闲、剧情丰富、视觉小说</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/11（暂无中文）</p><p>一款视觉小说，当你厌倦了目前的生活的时候，突然发现自己有一天变成了一只猫，还多了一只大公鸡作为朋友。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3562682_SXbHao.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3562682_T43J6u.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3562682_J6rHS7.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1235400/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Path of the Sramana</h4><p>关键字：免费、动作、冒险</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/11（暂无中文）</p><p>一款免费的平台动作游戏。</p><p>玩家要跟随着一位年轻的萨满巫师穿越灵魂世界，寻找她父亲的灵魂。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-Sramana5158oR.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3612822_Jq3lGf.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3612822_BbN2ks.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3612822_ezbM9x.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1231530/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>Gloomy Eyes</h4><p>关键字：免费、冒险、剧情丰富</p><p>发行日期：2020/03/11（<strong>中文支持</strong>）</p><p>故事讲述一个总是和群体格格不入的小男孩 Gloomy，因为偷了村长的东西，不得不逃入森林躲避赏金猎人，在过程中与小女孩 Nena 意外展开一段纯纯的爱。</p><p>咕噜米的眼睛是一部能在 6Dof VR 眼镜上使用，以及使用 3D 即时运算的 VR 动画电影。</p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/pic-gloomy5948sw.gif" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3613230_XIIfK9.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3613230_cnKJJM.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p><img src="https://hive.indienova.com/farm/article/picture/2020/03/img-3613230_c9akab.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dib" class="aligncenter"></p><p class="hidden-xs"><iframe src="https://store.steampowered.com/widget/1111620/" frameborder="0" style="width: 100%; height: 220px;"></iframe></p><h4>下半部分</h4><p>下半部分将于明日准时送到！</p><div class="text-center"><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="290" height="450" src="https://indienova.com/widget/indie-game-news/guide20-0309-0315-part-2/"></iframe></div>
